content: I am using your app. When I take a image and pinch zoom it then it shows cancer , but if zoom is not done then it doesn't show the cancer.  Whether zoom is allowed or not ? Thanks for your reply. I have sent my images at the email given at the developer contact
replyContent: Hello Sunil, The zoom can be used as long as focus is not lost on the sample, so you tell us that you have obtained a false positive when the quality of the image is lost when zooming.  In the case of your device, we recommend that you fit the skin area well and skip zooming.  We hope we have been able to help you. Kind regards.
